name: Galactic Domination
Text: 'Deploy on table.  Flagship and Endor Shield are canceled.  You may not deploy [Independent] or [Trade Federation] starships.  Once per turn, may use 1 Force to deploy an Executor site or a battleground system from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  While Flagship Operations on Executor: its power may not be reduced, your Force drains at battleground systems = 3, your TIE Assault Squadron may deploy without replacement (deploy = 3), and, wherever you have a TIE with a capital starship, draw one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.  Your cards add no more than 2 to the destiny, power, and forfeit of your squadrons.',
